Solved it by using `addEmbeddingToMemory` from `messageManager` as value for embedding with full its correct content
```ts
let newMemory: Memory = {
      userId: _message.agentId,
      agentId: _message.agentId,
      roomId: _message.roomId,
      content: {
          text: responseText,
          action: "NEWS_RESPONSE",
          source: _message.content.source
      } as Content
  };
newMemory = await runtime.messageManager.addEmbeddingToMemory(newMemory);
await runtime.messageManager.createMemory(newMemory);
```

